00:33:26,253 --> 00:33:27,894
If you look at reviews of Fantastic Entraption,

530
00:33:27,914 --> 00:33:30,255
you'll see that it's like a free-to-play game.

531
00:33:30,515 --> 00:33:33,316
And maybe there's a little extra stuff if you pay for it,

532
00:33:33,356 --> 00:33:35,056
but I'm not totally sure what it is.

533
00:33:35,657 --> 00:33:39,618
And so I think that's, obviously,

534
00:33:39,658 --> 00:33:41,278
that worked well for Fantastic Entraption.

535
00:33:42,259 --> 00:33:44,780
It's impossible to know if my conversion rate

536
00:33:45,320 --> 00:33:50,442
would have been higher at the time, but I think now I'm thinking about moving paywalls

