00:35:16,992 --> 00:35:19,694
And I think a lot of indies have problems with that,

563
00:35:20,074 --> 00:35:22,095
and they'll kind of not as much interest

564
00:35:22,135 --> 00:35:24,036
in the business side of things and the monetization

565
00:35:24,076 --> 00:35:24,637
side of things.

566
00:35:26,938 --> 00:35:31,020
Certainly for me, PayPal was the easiest single thing

567
00:35:31,040 --> 00:35:32,501
to implement and then kind of forget about it.

568
00:35:32,581 --> 00:35:36,284
You are absolutely on the nose in that I'm leaving

569
00:35:36,304 --> 00:35:37,184
a lot of money on the table.

