00:39:46,207 --> 00:39:50,049
But it turns out you spend a lot more time kind of digging through levels and tweaking

635
00:39:50,089 --> 00:39:56,232
levels and kind of doing editor work on levels that people submit.

636
00:39:56,852 --> 00:40:00,914
And in the end, it's probably better just writing your own content for yourself.

